resumes.desc: Worked within a startup to help with their data extraction through the implementation of NLP best practices.

One of 2% of applicants selected for 10-week, 450-hour ML bootcamp. Created a Render web app that allowed users to classify waste via a pre-trained PyTorch CNN. In addition, integrated a feedback mechanism with Google Cloud Storage in order to mitigate future sampling bias by populating the training data with new images from the feedback given.

Established a software development internship program where I communicated between management and three interns. Collaborated on an application allowing students to sign in and out while maintaining data for our marketing team.
